OL,5, A top UK surfer has slammed her sport  
OL,6, for relying on boards and wetsuits     
OL,7, mass-produced from petrochemicals that 
OL,8, create tonnes of waste every year.     
OL,10,FSeven times British women's champion   
OL,11,FLucy Campbell told the BBC the top     
OL,12,Fbrands "need to change".               
OL,14,FDespite surfing's eco-friendly image,  
OL,15,Fit uses plastic boards covered in toxic
OL,16,Fresins and non-biodegradable wetsuits. 
OL,18,FThe industry says it is developing new 
OL,19,Fsustainable boards and the world's     
OL,20,Ffirst fully recycled wetsuit.          
